causing more heat waves, and, possibly, more

00:03:47.459 --> 00:03:48.459
deaths.

00:03:48.459 --> 00:03:52.620
When the heat is on, make sure you stay in
the shade, cool off, and allow your sweat

00:03:52.620 --> 00:03:54.019
to evaporate.

00:03:54.019 --> 00:04:25.000
Stay cool folks.

